class:: NdMSpaceSpec
categories:: NdM
summary:: Lightweight builder/spec for NdM creation inside NdMSpace.

DESCRIPTION::
NdMSpaceSpec is a lightweight spec holder created from a Function via fromFunction.
It stores func/outBus/fadeTime/autoPlay/tagBuffer/dbgValue and provides chainable builders.
NdMSpace uses this spec to create/configure NdM nodes.

CLASSMETHODS::
method:: fromFunction
Create a spec from a UGen function.
argument:: inFunc
Function producing the node UGen graph.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec
discussion::
Initializes outBus=nil, fadeTime=0, autoPlay=false, tagBuffer=nil.

INSTANCEMETHODS::
method:: out
Set outBus (Integer/Array/Bus/nil). Reject NdMSpace instance.
argument:: outBusIn
Out-bus target.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec
discussion::
If outBusIn is an NdMSpace instance, throws an Error.

method:: fade
Set fade time (seconds).
argument:: fadeTimeIn
Fade duration.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec

method:: play
Mark autoPlay=true (consumed later by NdMSpace).
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec
discussion::
Also emits traceBegin/tracePush/traceEnd when inside an active NdMSpace.

method:: o
Alias of out.
argument:: outTarget
Out-bus target.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec

method:: f
Alias of fade.
argument:: fadeTimeIn
Fade duration.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec

method:: p
Alias of play.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec

method:: tag
Buffer a tag to be applied after NdM creation.
argument:: tagSymbol
Tag symbol.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec
discussion::
tagBuffer is created lazily; Array.add requires reassignment.

method:: untag
Remove a buffered tag.
argument:: tagSymbol
Tag symbol.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec

method:: t
Alias of tag.
argument:: tagSymbol
Tag symbol.
returns:: NdMSpaceSpec

method:: applyTagsTo
Apply buffered tags to an NdM instance (post-create hook).
argument:: ndmInstance
Target NdM instance.
returns:: nil
discussion::
Iterates tagBuffer and calls ndmInstance.tag(tagItem).

method:: dbg
Get or set dbgValue.

argument:: value
If nil, returns current dbgValue; otherwise sets dbgValue.

returns:: Object
discussion::
When used as setter, returns this; when used as getter, returns dbgValue.
The underlying property setter exists as dbg_ but is documented here as dbg.